title: Georgia Boot Marshland Unisex Alloy Toe Pull-On Duck Boot
features: Alloy safety toe for lightweight protection
description: Take on water, muck and mayhem with the Marshland by Georgia Boot. This alloy toe pull-on duck boot is ready for the elements. This 10-inch duck style boot has an upper is constructed from premium SPR leather, leather pull loops and a cooling fiber-infused lining. The polyurethane and cushioning memory foam AMP LT insole is removable and provides your feet with all day comfort.This duck boot features a lightweight Ergo-Fit alloy toe cap, designed to give your toes a better range of motion, meeting ASTM F2413 protective toe classification for safety toe footwear. And meets the same standard for electrical hazards. A slip and oil-resisting rubber outsole and waterproof rubber shell are affixed with durable vulcanized rubber construction. Classic duck boot style with protective features - pick up your pair of the Georgia Boot Marshland protective toe work boots today.
